title: Re: ‘Get lost lady!’: Twitter upset with Rep. Debbie Wasserman Schultz over impeachment talk
text:
— Jay O. Spinner (@309_470) February 16, 2017 @ErinBurnett @OutFrontCNN @DWStweets DWS should hang her head in shame! Should be prosecuted for rigging primary! Get lost lady! 
— Allen Vollbrecht (@allenvollbrecht) February 16, 2017 @OutFrontCNN @ErinBurnett @CNN Please stop lending legitimacy to the disgraced, unethical @DWStweets ;she's lost all credibility! #DEMExit 
— K~OM (@niall15) February 16, 2017 @OutFrontCNN @AC360 @DWStweets @ErinBurnett @CNN She's right. And she she also still makes me sick to my stomach and should go away! 
— Powerful Snowflake (@ceehope) February 16, 2017 @OutFrontCNN @DWStweets @CNN @ErinBurnett saying she lost her job because of Russian hacking was a poor choice of words. She did much more
